code: @Test public void testToString() {     ErrorMessage em = new ErrorMessage(new RuntimeException("foo")).     String emString = em.toString().     assertThat(emString, not(containsString("original"))).     em = new ErrorMessage(new RuntimeException("foo"), new GenericMessage<>("bar")).     emString = em.toString().     assertThat(emString, containsString("original")).     assertThat(emString, containsString(em.getOriginalMessage().toString())). }
